features: 【Good Quality】: The car battery terminal cleaning brush is made of premium stainless steel, steel wire and plastic material, which are evenly distributed. The stainless steel material has the advantage of being anti-rust and anti-corrosion, strong and durable, and can be used for quite a long time.

【Main Function】: The main function of the car battery terminal brush is cleaning your car battery's dust, rust, stains, etc., so as to make a good contact between your car and the car battery. During cleaning, the brush is not easily damaged, resistant to scratches and wear, and will not damage objects' surface.

【4-in-1 Design】: The car battery terminal cleaning brush totally has 4 places for cleaning your car battery terminal, which are 2 holes and 2 brush tips. The round brush head in the middle can be placed on the protruding part of the parts to clean around the terminals. The brush tip on the end can go deep inside the battery terminals to clean the rust and stains inside.

【Easy to Carry】: The length of the car battery cleaning brush is merely 7.87 inches, and its weight is just 70 g. This specification is so small and lightweight, portable to carry with you, and it does not take up space when used. Besides, it is in a strip shape and is easy to store.

【Wide Application】: This double-head car battery brush has a wide range of compatibility, can be applied in cleaning most vehicles' batteries, as well as cleaning steel parts, mechanical parts, unfinished metal parts, and many other parts.
